This list discusses on Japanese Debian system,
for example, how to use Japanese on Debian system,
and how to integrate Debian JP Packages into Debian
in mainly English. However, we encourage for non
native Japanese to write Japanese mail on this
list. For native Japanese, Debian JP Project provides
several mailing-list discussing on Debian system in
Japanese. See http://www.debian.or.jp/MailingList.html
